&lt;p>&lt;a href="https://i.imgur.com/zvLzrAm.jpeg">How to Realign Higanbana&lt;/a>&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Samurai Stat Priority</title><link>https://www.thebalanceffxiv.com/jobs/melee/samurai/stat-priority/</link><pubDate>Sun, 18 Aug 2024 07:44:19 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.thebalanceffxiv.com/jobs/melee/samurai/stat-priority/</guid><description>&lt;p>Based on current gear available to us, if you&amp;rsquo;re not using &lt;a href="https://xivgear.app/">XIVGear&lt;/a> to figure out what melds are best for your specific situation the below is a decent blind meld order to follow: SKS (to tier)* &amp;gt; Crit &amp;gt; Det &amp;gt;= DH&lt;br>
